When we are loading componnet on demand or lazy loading reactg tries to suspend it.To handle this we need to use Suspense, wrap our componemt in suspense componemt.

When shoud I create a hook--- When we need state  tto store and resuable logic in oyur application.


Note: Never dynamically load your component inside a component